on the hunt in the Chugach

AK has always been a bucket list / dream trip of mine. last spring I got a call on Friday evening, booked my ticket, packed gear and flew out at 6am on monday. I thought my winter was over but by Wednesday I was being dropped on knife edge ridges with cornices on both sides hunting for angles.

we were graced with blue skies & dry powder for 2 days w/ @pointsnorthheli — couldn’t have been better. beyond stoked to share a few stills.

thank you to @pointsnorthheli for a trip of a lifetime, @akhelipro for the top notch flying, @tinovillanueva for showing us rookies how it’s done & of course @simon.hillis & @madisonnnrose for crushing in front of the lens 🤝
